This is, surprisely, onPHP repository (or just checkout).
UTF8 is mandatory.

SVN: http://svn.shadanakar.org/
Web: http://onphp.shadanakar.org/

IRC:

	irc.freenode.org
	#onPHP-dev (koi8-r is mandatory for russian speaking people)

Lists:

	General discussion in russian language:
	
		onphp-dev-ru+subscribe@lists.shadanakar.org

	SVN-commits:
	
		onphp-commits+subscribe@lists.shadanakar.org
	

Quite useful information:

	$Id$

Quick start:

	cp src/global.inc.php.tpl src/global.inc.php

	include copied file in your script and enjoy
